data.description: Beautifully updated home on one acre. 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. All on one level. Open concept living room, kitchen, and dining room. The views of the Catalina Mountains are breathtaking! Large fenced in backyard, and a double carport. Also full hook-up for a recreation vehicle. Close to the convenience of town, with a country feel. Come see this remarkable property today!
